{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-1/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"b10c0155-102d-5f8e-9f2a-d84671d49cee","excerpt":"개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 1 - 기본 세팅 개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 2 - Tailwind CSS 적용 개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 3 - 페이징(Pagination) 적용 개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 4 - 댓글(giscus…","html":"<ul>\n<li><strong>개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 1 - 기본 세팅</strong></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 2 - Tailwind CSS 적용</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 3 - 페이징(Pagination) 적용</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-4/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 4 - 댓글(giscus) 적용</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-5/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 5 - 블로그(GitHub Pages) 배포</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whitepaek.com/posts/2024/01/gatsby-blog-start-6/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby) 블로그 만들기 6 - 사용자 지정 도메인 적용</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">개츠비(Gatsby)</a>로 블로그 만드는 과정을 제가 경험한 내용으로 설명드릴게요.</p>\n<p>개츠비를 기반으로 블로그를 처음부터 하나씩 세팅하기에는 까다로워요. 특히 저처럼 이해도가 전혀 없는 상태라면, 시작조차 못할 수 있어요.\n그래서 저는 개츠비에서 공식적으로 제공해 주는 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/starters/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">gatsby-starter-blog</a>를 이용해서 세팅을 해주도록 할게요.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-blog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">깃허브(github)에서 gatsby-starter-blog 설치</a>하기 전에 Node.js와 gatsby-cli를 설치해야 해요.<br>\n저는 윈도우(windows)가 설치되어 있는 컴퓨터가 없기 때문에 macOS를 기준으로 설명드릴게요.</p>\n<p>Node.js를 설치하기 전에 macOS에서 필수라고 볼 수 있는 패키지 관리자 <a href=\"https://brew.sh/ko/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Homebrew</a>가 설치되어 있어야 해요.<br>\n(설치가 안 되어 있다면 1번부터 따라 하고, 되어 있다면 2번부터 따라 하면 돼요.)</p>\n<h2>1. Homebrew 설치</h2>\n<p>터미널(terminal)을 실행하여 아래 명령어를 입력해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ /bin/bash <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-c</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"<span class=\"token variable\"><span class=\"token variable\">$(</span><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-fsSL</span> https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh<span class=\"token variable\">)</span></span>\"</span>\n$ xcode-select <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--install</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/833c3ca7642af220ba8e0c9c019e6c60/d50e7/homebrew-install.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.45569620253164%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[1] Homebrew 설치\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/833c3ca7642af220ba8e0c9c019e6c60/f058b/homebrew-install.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/833c3ca7642af220ba8e0c9c019e6c60/c26ae/homebrew-install.png 158w,\n/static/833c3ca7642af220ba8e0c9c019e6c60/6bdcf/homebrew-install.png 315w,\n/static/833c3ca7642af220ba8e0c9c019e6c60/f058b/homebrew-install.png 630w,\n/static/833c3ca7642af220ba8e0c9c019e6c60/40601/homebrew-install.png 945w,\n/static/833c3ca7642af220ba8e0c9c019e6c60/78612/homebrew-install.png 1260w,\n/static/833c3ca7642af220ba8e0c9c019e6c60/d50e7/homebrew-install.png 2280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[1] Homebrew 설치</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>2. Node.js 설치</h2>\n<p>Homebrew 설치가 완료되었다면, 터미널에서 아래 명령어를 참고하여 Node.js를 설치해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token function\">node</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1082c231561b7af4d44e66a6d7247f85/d50e7/node-install.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.45569620253164%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[2] Node.js 설치\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1082c231561b7af4d44e66a6d7247f85/f058b/node-install.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1082c231561b7af4d44e66a6d7247f85/c26ae/node-install.png 158w,\n/static/1082c231561b7af4d44e66a6d7247f85/6bdcf/node-install.png 315w,\n/static/1082c231561b7af4d44e66a6d7247f85/f058b/node-install.png 630w,\n/static/1082c231561b7af4d44e66a6d7247f85/40601/node-install.png 945w,\n/static/1082c231561b7af4d44e66a6d7247f85/78612/node-install.png 1260w,\n/static/1082c231561b7af4d44e66a6d7247f85/d50e7/node-install.png 2280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[2] Node.js 설치</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>3. gatsby-cli 설치</h2>\n<p>Node.js 설치가 완료되었으면, 터미널에서 아래 명령어를 참고하여 gatsby-cli를 설치해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-g</span> gatsby-cli</code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/43c75cb67560e440893ef7a78198266f/d50e7/gatsby-cli-install.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.45569620253164%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[3] gatsby-cli 설치\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/43c75cb67560e440893ef7a78198266f/f058b/gatsby-cli-install.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/43c75cb67560e440893ef7a78198266f/c26ae/gatsby-cli-install.png 158w,\n/static/43c75cb67560e440893ef7a78198266f/6bdcf/gatsby-cli-install.png 315w,\n/static/43c75cb67560e440893ef7a78198266f/f058b/gatsby-cli-install.png 630w,\n/static/43c75cb67560e440893ef7a78198266f/40601/gatsby-cli-install.png 945w,\n/static/43c75cb67560e440893ef7a78198266f/78612/gatsby-cli-install.png 1260w,\n/static/43c75cb67560e440893ef7a78198266f/d50e7/gatsby-cli-install.png 2280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[3] gatsby-cli 설치</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>4. gatsby-starter-blog 설치</h2>\n<p>gatsby-cli까지 설치가 완료되었으면, 아래 명령어를 참고하여 gatsby-starter-blog 프로젝트를 설치할게요.\n<code class=\"language-text\">cd</code> 명령어로 본인이 설치하고 싶은 디렉터리 위치로 이동하고, 아래 명령어에서 <strong>my-blog-starter</strong> 위치에 본인이 하고 싶은 프로젝트 이름을 작성해 주세요.\n저는 설명을 위해서 공식 문서 예시를 그대로 진행할게요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> ~/Downloads/\n$ gatsby new my-blog-starter https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby-starter-blog</code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7af17758f08e3da160a36b5c09a4f900/d50e7/gatsby-starter-blog-install.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.45569620253164%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[4] gatsby-starter-blog 설치\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/7af17758f08e3da160a36b5c09a4f900/f058b/gatsby-starter-blog-install.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7af17758f08e3da160a36b5c09a4f900/c26ae/gatsby-starter-blog-install.png 158w,\n/static/7af17758f08e3da160a36b5c09a4f900/6bdcf/gatsby-starter-blog-install.png 315w,\n/static/7af17758f08e3da160a36b5c09a4f900/f058b/gatsby-starter-blog-install.png 630w,\n/static/7af17758f08e3da160a36b5c09a4f900/40601/gatsby-starter-blog-install.png 945w,\n/static/7af17758f08e3da160a36b5c09a4f900/78612/gatsby-starter-blog-install.png 1260w,\n/static/7af17758f08e3da160a36b5c09a4f900/d50e7/gatsby-starter-blog-install.png 2280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[4] gatsby-starter-blog 설치</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>5. gatsby-starter-blog 실행</h2>\n<p>gatsby-starter-blog 설치가 완료되었으면 실행해 보도록 할게요.\nVisual Studio Code 또는 웹스톰(webstorm) 도구(tool)로 설치한 gatsby-starter-blog 프로젝트를 열어주세요.\n저는 웹스톰으로 할게요. 웹스톰을 실행하고 우측 상단에 Open 버튼을 클릭해서 프로젝트를 열어주세요.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1e3c43b5bc6c803ab1589b71a3ec2dda/18d55/webstorm-blog-open.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 72.15189873417721%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[5] 웹스톰에서 gatsby-starter-blog 프로젝트 열기\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1e3c43b5bc6c803ab1589b71a3ec2dda/f058b/webstorm-blog-open.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1e3c43b5bc6c803ab1589b71a3ec2dda/c26ae/webstorm-blog-open.png 158w,\n/static/1e3c43b5bc6c803ab1589b71a3ec2dda/6bdcf/webstorm-blog-open.png 315w,\n/static/1e3c43b5bc6c803ab1589b71a3ec2dda/f058b/webstorm-blog-open.png 630w,\n/static/1e3c43b5bc6c803ab1589b71a3ec2dda/40601/webstorm-blog-open.png 945w,\n/static/1e3c43b5bc6c803ab1589b71a3ec2dda/78612/webstorm-blog-open.png 1260w,\n/static/1e3c43b5bc6c803ab1589b71a3ec2dda/18d55/webstorm-blog-open.png 2470w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[5] 웹스톰에서 gatsby-starter-blog 프로젝트 열기</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>gatsby-starter-blog 프로젝트를 열었으면, 아래 이미지처럼 package.json 파일을 열고 44번 라인의 <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby develop</code>을 실행해주세요.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d58b3d9218cbaa0e6be1dab5c883a0d0/b918a/gatsby-develop-run.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 71.51898734177216%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[5-1] 웹스톰에서 gatsby-starter-blog 실행\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d58b3d9218cbaa0e6be1dab5c883a0d0/f058b/gatsby-develop-run.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d58b3d9218cbaa0e6be1dab5c883a0d0/c26ae/gatsby-develop-run.png 158w,\n/static/d58b3d9218cbaa0e6be1dab5c883a0d0/6bdcf/gatsby-develop-run.png 315w,\n/static/d58b3d9218cbaa0e6be1dab5c883a0d0/f058b/gatsby-develop-run.png 630w,\n/static/d58b3d9218cbaa0e6be1dab5c883a0d0/40601/gatsby-develop-run.png 945w,\n/static/d58b3d9218cbaa0e6be1dab5c883a0d0/78612/gatsby-develop-run.png 1260w,\n/static/d58b3d9218cbaa0e6be1dab5c883a0d0/b918a/gatsby-develop-run.png 2780w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">[5-1] 웹스톰에서 gatsby-starter-blog 실행</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>또는 터미널에서 위에서 설치한 프로젝트 위치로 이동 후 gatsby 명령어를 실행해 주세요.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> ~/Downloads/my-blog-starter/\n$ gatsby develop</code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6628cd228f87528311cdea7f922225fd/a3a74/gatsby-develop-command.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 79.74683544303798%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"[5-2] 터미널에서 gatsby-starter-blog 실행\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6628cd228f87528311